medicalrecords

Class MedicalRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • medicalrecords.MedicalRecord

  • public class MedicalRecord
extends java.lang.Object
    The MedicalRecord class represents the medical history of a patient. It contains details such as the patient ID, diagnoses, and treatments. This class allows adding and retrieving medical information related to a patient.
